<MELItem itemNbr="22-11-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-22-11-01.1.2-22-11-01">
<Title>Autoflight Function</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be dispatched with AUTOFLIGHT FUNCTION faults provided the A/P DISENGAGE bar is verified to operate normally.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Verify that the A/P DISENGAGE bar operates normally. (AMM DDG 22-11-01).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>With flaps up, engage the autopilot.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Disconnect the autopilot with the A/P DISENGAGE bar.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Confirm that the autopilot disconnects, the AUTOPILOT DISC warning message is displayed, the aural is activated, and at least one master warning light is illuminated.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<Para>The autopilot system has lost redundancy but operates normally.</Para>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>